<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>KTM 390 Duke R</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f5f6fa;
    color:#222;
}

.container{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:20px;
}

header{
    background:#fff;
    padding:15px 30px;
    box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    z-index:100;
}

.logo{
    font-size:24px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#ff6600;
}

.hero{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr;
    gap:25px;
    margin-top:20px;
}

.card{
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:20px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
}

.main-image{
    width:100%;
    height:420px;
    object-fit:cover;
    border-radius:12px;
}

.thumbnail-row{
    display:flex;
    gap:10px;
    margin-top:12px;
}

.thumb{
    width:90px;
    height:60px;
    border-radius:8px;
    cursor:pointer;
    object-fit:cover;
    border:2px solid transparent;
}

.thumb.active{
    border-color:#ff6600;
}

.bike-title{
    font-size:34px;
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.rating{
    color:#f4b400;
    font-size:18px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.price{
    font-size:34px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#111;
}

.sub-price{
    color:#666;
    margin-top:5px;
}

.btns{
    display:flex;
    gap:12px;
    margin-top:20px;
}

.btn{
    flex:1;
    padding:14px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-weight:600;
    cursor:pointer;
}

.primary{
    background:#ff6600;
    color:white;
}

.secondary{
    background:#eee;
}

.specs{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    gap:15px;
    margin-top:25px;
}

.spec-box{
    background:white;
    padding:18px;
    text-align:center;
    border-radius:12px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
}

.spec-value{
    font-size:24px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#ff6600;
}

.spec-label{
    color:#666;
    margin-top:8px;
}

.tabs{
    display:flex;
    gap:15px;
    margin-top:35px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.tab{
    background:white;
    border:none;
    padding:12px 20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

.tab.active{
    background:#ff6600;
    color:white;
}

.tab-content{
    margin-top:20px;
}

.content-panel{
    display:none;
}

.content-panel.active{
    display:block;
}

.feature-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
    gap:15px;
}

.feature-item{
    background:white;
    padding:18px;
    border-radius:12px;
}

.spec-table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:collapse;
    background:white;
    border-radius:12px;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.spec-table td{
    padding:14px;
    border-bottom:1px solid #eee;
}

.review{
    background:white;
    padding:18px;
    border-radius:12px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.emi-box{
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:12px;
}

input[type=range]{
    width:100%;
    margin:15px 0;
}

.emi-result{
    font-size:32px;
    color:#ff6600;
    font-weight:700;
}

.footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px;
    color:#666;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.hero{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.specs{
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
}

.feature-grid{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
}
}

@media(max-width:600px){

.specs{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.bike-title{
    font-size:28px;
}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">BikeZone</div>
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="hero">

<div class="card">

<img id="mainImage"
class="main-image"
src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558981806-ec527fa84c39?w=1200"
alt="bike">

<div class="thumbnail-row">

<img class="thumb active"
src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558981806-ec527fa84c39?w=500">

<img class="thumb"
src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=500">

<img class="thumb"
src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511919884226-fd3cad34687c?w=500">

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h1 class="bike-title">KTM 390 Duke R</h1>

<div class="rating">
★★★★★ 4.8 (1,254 Reviews)
</div>

<div class="price">₹3.38 Lakh</div>
<div class="sub-price">Avg. Ex-Showroom Price</div>

<div class="btns">
<button class="btn primary">Get Offers</button>
<button class="btn secondary">Book Test Ride</button>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="specs">

<div class="spec-box">
<div class="spec-value">399cc</div>
<div class="spec-label">Engine</div>
</div>

<div class="spec-box">
<div class="spec-value">46 HP</div>
<div class="spec-label">Power</div>
</div>

<div class="spec-box">
<div class="spec-value">39 Nm</div>
<div class="spec-label">Torque</div>
</div>

<div class="spec-box">
<div class="spec-value">29 kmpl</div>
<div class="spec-label">Mileage</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="tabs">
<button class="tab active" data-tab="overview">Overview</button>
<button class="tab" data-tab="specs">Specifications</button>
<button class="tab" data-tab="features">Features</button>
<button class="tab" data-tab="reviews">Reviews</button>
</div>

<div class="tab-content">

<div class="content-panel active" id="overview">

<div class="card">
<h2>About KTM 390 Duke R</h2>
<br>
<p>
The KTM 390 Duke R is a premium naked street motorcycle
featuring a powerful 399cc liquid-cooled engine, aggressive styling,
TFT display, ride modes, traction control, and premium suspension.
Built for performance enthusiasts, it offers a thrilling riding experience.
</p>
</div>

<br>

<div class="emi-box">
<h2>EMI Calculator</h2>

<input id="loanRange"
type="range"
min="100000"
max="500000"
step="10000"
value="338000">

<p>Loan Amount:
<strong id="loanAmount">₹338000</strong>
</p>

<br>

<div>
Monthly EMI:
<div class="emi-result" id="emiResult">₹7,110</div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="content-panel" id="specs">

<table class="spec-table">
<tr>
<td>Engine</td>
<td>399cc Liquid Cooled</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Power</td>
<td>46 HP</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Torque</td>
<td>39 Nm</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Gearbox</td>
<td>6-Speed</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Fuel Tank</td>
<td>15 Litres</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Weight</td>
<td>168 Kg</td>
</tr>
</table>

</div>

<div class="content-panel" id="features">

<div class="feature-grid">

<div class="feature-item">
✅ TFT Digital Display
</div>

<div class="feature-item">
✅ Quick Shifter
</div>

<div class="feature-item">
✅ Ride Modes
</div>

<div class="feature-item">
✅ Dual Channel ABS
</div>

<div class="feature-item">
✅ Traction Control
</div>

<div class="feature-item">
✅ LED Lighting
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="content-panel" id="reviews">

<div class="review">
<h3>Rahul Sharma</h3>
★★★★★
<p>Excellent performance and handling. One of the best bikes in this segment.</p>
</div>

<div class="review">
<h3>Amit Verma</h3>
★★★★☆
<p>Powerful engine and premium features. Mileage could be slightly better.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
